_header: Jesu most sweetest of any thing / To love Thou I have great longing
_description: ‘A song of loue to owre lorde Iesu Criste’ — seventy monorhyming quatrains

HarRich22.First Lines:
Ihesu most swettest of any þyngeTo loue ȝow I haue grete
                    longyngeþerfore I byseche ȝow heuyn kyngemake me of
                    ȝowre loue to haue felinge…
HarRich22.Last Lines:
…Euir myrþe blysse & glad lykyngeGlorious Ihesu god
                    þerto vs brynge
HarRich22.Attributed Title:
Here bygynniþ a songe of loue to owre lorde Ihesu christe (f.
                    72)
